description:
Sonic Universe (A Sonic comic series) has officially announced they will continue where the Sonic Underground series left off and will even give it A proper ending! More info here!

http://www.sonicretro.org/2012/10/sonic-underground-to-be-finished-in-comic-form/#comments

comments.text: People, the real people to blame for Sonic Underground's epilogue not coming could be with Sega themselves.  After the Penders lawsuit, Sega forced Archie to reboot the comic universe and forced them to abide by mandates which have been strengthened.  One of them is the game characters cannot have family members, and since Sonic has a mother and a twin brother and sister in this series, Sega is not going to allow it.
